{{Quote|As you have discovered, this island has many old wounds. And I'm, afraid the cycle of violence is starting again. I have one more favor to ask of you.|Elder Runara, to the adventurers.}}

In the {{YearlinkName|1481}}, a group of five [[adventurer]]s came to Dragon's Rest from the city of [[Neverwinter]]. They were ferried across by the scoundrel captain named [[Drauz|Drauz the Dreg]] from the city's [[Neverwinter/Blacklake District|Blacklake District]].{{Cite document/Before the Storm}}

Elder Runara observed the adventurers with the hope they would prove trustworthy enough to retrieve her lost [[wyrmling]] Aidron from the disgruntled dragon [[Sparkrender]].
